<div class="footer">
  <h3 class="footer-h">NOW YOU KNOW<br>HOW IT WORKS.</h3>
  <p class="footer-txt">You'll still feel the emotions. That's fine — you're human. But now there's a tiny voice in the back of your head that says: wait. who built this feeling? That voice is media literacy.</p>
